{"tid":653581,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"求推介好用嘅記帳app","createTime":"2018-05-05T00:36:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T19:21:06.000Z","uid":34802,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"d24a5fce042583c24b678e5a7ef27f6e5d5b033c","tid":653581,"uid":34802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T00:36:41.000Z","msg":"我用Android 機<br />\n用咗cwmoney 專業版3年<br />\n我覺得相比其他app，圖表功能比較弱<br />\n想轉過另一隻<br />\n各位巴打有咩app推介<br />\n最好嗰個app 有專案功能<br />\n我就唔太介意複雜， 最好功能多啲啦<br />\n<br />\n有巴打提過呢啲:<br />\nMoney Manager Next - Expense &amp; Budget - 唔同account, 唔同category 計budget都有<br />\nMoney Pro<br />\nMoneyWiz<br />\nMoze - 記帳，彈指之間<br />\n秒速記帳 1SecMoney<br />\n隨手記 - 雖然係大陸app, 可以自訂支出同埋budget 的分類sub分類，仲可以set係咩信用卡銀行戶口<br />\n圈子帳本<br />\nWeple Money Pro - 簡單，快<br />\n<br />\n你哋用開邊個呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c410470d99dd297fdbadf54743ed33f4326fed","tid":653581,"uid":117947,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T00:42:48.000Z","msg":"我用緊鯊魚記帳，nexus money(舊版）"},{"pid":"3a4d4974df6b965150d68f8f7e821f4256d34362","tid":653581,"uid":51932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T00:47:36.000Z","msg":"Ynab 用咗幾年"},{"pid":"b06b6613da5d0c2c1c03801f2ea8abe24204842b","tid":653581,"uid":34802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T00:49:00.000Z","msg":"你哋覺得Andromoney好唔好用呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c1a6654e30f9b9cab1e503b3028db89c35aba65","tid":653581,"uid":25659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T00:49:54.000Z","msg":"用緊ahorro"},{"pid":"d2aaaae8d161d9ecc2204eaf06698648ff4c7eed","tid":653581,"uid":81211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c1a6654e30f9b9cab1e503b3028db89c35aba65","tid":653581,"uid":25659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T00:49:54.000Z","msg":"用緊ahorro"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T00